title: No Equipment 20 Minute Bodyweight Workout | Follow Along
description:
Bored of the same old workout routines? Try 7 days FREE on my training app, LEVEL UP your routine and LEVEL UP you results 👉 https://www.jtmfit.com/

Today 's workout is a 20 minute full body workout that require ZERO equipment. All you will need is your bodyweight!

This is a full follow along workout that consists of 20 different exercises with no repeats.

We are going to perform each exercise for 45 seconds with 15 seconds rest in between exercises. 1 total set.

If you need to modify the workout you can do a few different time structures.

40 seconds ON - 20 seconds OFF
35 seconds ON - 25 seconds OFF
30 seconds ON - 30 seconds OFF

Give this workout your best effort and let's torch some calories 💪🏻

#bodyweightworkout #athomeworkout #noequipmentworkout
